This is the DocBook source of the Video For Linux Two API Specification.

The latest version is part of the v4l-dvb master repository:

  http://linuxtv.org/hg/v4l-dvb

If you have ideas or questions regarding V4L2, please try the
linux-media mailing list. Information on how to join is here:

  http://www.linuxtv.org/lists.php

The Makefile supports the following targets:

html-single	A single HTML file (default)
html		Tree of HTML files
pdf		A PDF file
coffeebreak 	All of the above

Note: the V4L1_API.html is here just for reference. The V4L2 API replaces
V4L1.
